title: S16 Ep110: Supernatural News/Parashare: Ghosts of 9/11 Edition
itunes:title: Supernatural News/Parashare: Ghosts of 9/11 Edition
description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare Ghosts of 9/11 Edition

Dave & Tim are back with your Supernatural News from around the world. This week we report on alleged. claims of reincarnated victims from 9/11,  The Sopranos vs The Supernatural, The Lost Boys Return, but should they? Paranormal Activity: Next of Kin announced, a paranormal bomb scare and MORE plus your stories and emails.

Join Dave this weekend at The New Jersey ParaUnity Expo: https://www.newjerseyparaunityexpo.com/

Book a Cameo with Dave for the holidays, birthdays and more: https://bit.ly/3zteFIK
